Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, 6 o'clock exactly. After that mountain training, \NI always wake up at the exact same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Off I go. Time for morning training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? You're still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous. \NDon't drive while you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, I'm going too, on my \NThree-Wheeled Attack-Type Combat Vehicle Tricycle-kun. {攻撃型戦闘三輪車とらいしくん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, don't force yourself. \NIt's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Honmaru friends. Always suppo-po-po-port...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I've become a man that's suitable for Iyona-chan? {hope he means in the past tense, not "you think it'd be possible that ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have become!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, Iyona-chan said she loves me, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as for me, I also love Iyona-chan \Nmore than anything in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means this feeling is mutual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me till the end, Taru! \NI'm just getting to the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, Taru-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup, Iyona!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona, are you also training this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A volleyball match is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan's sweat is glistening beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Iyona-chan. I'll be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You keep up \Nthe good work too, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than anything in the world, \NI loved Honmaru-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what is it you're working towards now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm working on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that should be obvious by now. \NWhy does Iyona-chan even need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best to be fit for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Iyona-chan said \Nshe wants to become the wife of a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Marue-chan, when I grow up, \Nmy dream is to become a wife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To wear a pure white wedding dress, \Nand live with a kind and wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And have... Five or six children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm working hard to become a wonderful man, \None that's able to protect and comfort Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at me so intently with your big eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, I love you! \NI've been into you for an eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Since when have you been listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, did you put Hearer on me again?! {actually "since when did you put this on me?" but need to account for taru answering yeah}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! 'Cause I'm doing my best for Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan heard everything I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. Very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I mean... That was... \NIyona-chan, you heard him, right? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? What to do? I'm so screwed! Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already! I'll say it! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you! Let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Married!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan didn't actually love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! It's because Iyona-chan \Nis such a kind-hearted girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that it didn't matter who from the class dies, \Nshe'd say the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Harako died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually loved Harako-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Jabao died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually loved Jabao-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Korekiyo died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually loved Korekiyo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd definitely say the very same thing! {no clue what's first word}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how could I... How could I be such a naive fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so conceited, \Njumping to the wrong conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I've said all sorts of weird things, \Nshe'll hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate you...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, let's run after Iyona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to hate me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong. Iyona loves Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me understand Iyona's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do without you comforting me, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival! We'll rectify your obnoxious habits \Nwith an early morning marathon!{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, follow right after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up with a woman who's off her rocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama! Taru-sama, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You woke up so early to go for a jog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A good morning kiss for good boys. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't they lucky? Children are so innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you staring so suspiciously at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just thought about \Nhow you're always full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be? \NIt's all thanks to my great love for Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, I must be cheerful for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even if Taru came to hate you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Even if that dark day of history ever comes, {tlc, not sure what's this maijo, could be mainichi but kinda doesn't sit well}{I can't make sense of that word.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would still love Taru-sama until the end of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My love is not so uncertain \Nas to be shaken by something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would do the same for me, Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Me love Mimora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're {\i1}so{\i0} not getting away with it, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you slacking off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get going! Off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Iyona-chan came to hate me, \NI'll still love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll chase after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rather primitive fella. {guess, kinda hear tanjun there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan's magic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulled Iyona back with Attractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Raser?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Raser had seen his share of misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So he ended up looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him from you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've cherished it ever since, \Nalways keeping it close to heart.{/without separating from skin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In times of joy, or in times of grief, whenever I see Raser, \NI seem to always regain my motivation, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, even if you come to hate me, I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I would still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora, get your Limpy-kun out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it happened so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go skating together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, mood is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to give Iyona a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Honmaru-kun, you pervert, pervert, pervert!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to slack off as soon \Nas I turn my eyes away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A healthy mind comes from a healthy body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Taruruuto! I'll remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan was so upset about it, \Nfor real this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Honmaru, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you've got a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, you've nothing to apologize for. \NI should be the one to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru and Iyona made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At 10 o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Me wanna know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I do that a lot too!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet Iyona in person, \Nnot over the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use Promptelephone, \Nyou can see her in person right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been learning figure skating since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This - my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,With Promptelephone you can fit yourself \Ninto the phone mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you send yourself to the other end \Nvia the telephone wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done! That's one useful magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... The phone is getting very heavy, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Taru, how do we get out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We'll get out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two cannot fit through it at once, no sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me I'll stay like this forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Honmaru. \NIn ten minutes, my magic will wear off.{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to wait ten minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Taru-chan, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru got a date today!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's what happened! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Still happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Still happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Still happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear, Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After you finish cleaning, laundry, and shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget to do 100 push-ups and sit-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come bleh-ack soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if I had the time to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to exact my revenge on Taruruuto! {lit: make him know}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(253.6,248)\frz1.078\c&H6F4148&\bord0\blur0.4\b0}Nannosho Ice Arena
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mimora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it a double date, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, why do I have to wear something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going skating with Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For a daughter of the Kawai family, \Njust skating would never suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,wherever you go, you must skate \Nwith grace and splendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only outfit that would avail you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't allowed to go unless you wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the gentlemen's hearts would be yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Better already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are taking your time, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Iyona's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A staggering outfit, Iyona-chan!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona looking cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Taru-sama too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An outfit like that is a shortcut to catching a cold! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Amazing! Her white and clean skin is all out...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Honmaru drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't stare at me, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I do wonder why she chose \Nthat outfit in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are so inscrutable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is staring. \NI knew it would be embarrassing, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those looks are so scrutinizing! {/don't look at me so ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just skating around \Nin these clothes is embarrassing indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you take that chance to show off your skating techniques, the awe would displace embarrassment. {/embarrassment would be blown away}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool, Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a couple of cheap tricks. {/that much was easy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll skate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd find a thousand and one ways to fall! {/interesting way to fall}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sli-li-li-lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun! Everyone sli-li-li-lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Taru! \NYou can't play tricks on people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I slipped, so everyone should sli-li-li-lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In skating, falling is a foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, isn't there some magic \Nfor skating well without falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a complete zero in skating, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With this Balansolution, you'll be able to hold your balance perfectly and without falling. {バラン酢}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Me skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how well I can skate, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I feel like I can't fall at all! \NThis is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan... I'm here!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're so good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Having all this fun with Mimora-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Time to turn it around \Nwith the Transformation Belt! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn invisible and send him flying from behind! {/kick}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me an invisible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fall flat before Mimora-chan's eyes!{to (dramatically) fall over; to fall flat​}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll expose your most miserable side to her, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this, you parasite! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to Balansolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With spectacular midair turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just fell even deeper in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more spectacular this time, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! Thanks to the Balansolution, \NI even saved Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay for my humiliation as well, you ass! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, care to explain why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the work I tasked you with \Nwas abandoned, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, your nasty habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be rectified by any other means!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to... Ow! It hurts! \NThat's enough! Ah, Sensei! Forgive me! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, skating is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's the best ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, as long as I'm with you, \Nyou'll always be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... But Honmaru-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would you mind putting me down already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't need to be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not actually one bit heavy, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But I like it this way! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this haircut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your doing, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru, looking cool! \NSo brushy-brushy and nice! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's spiky-spiky and cold! \NThat's how my head is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to a New Year's party like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:22:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Greatest New Year Ever! {最高だぜお正月!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This better?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 69 \NThe Best New Year Ever! {最高だぜお正月!}
